#: plugin/framework/constants.py:287
msgid ""
"AI: I can edit or translate your document instantly with professional "
"formatting and color. Try me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu trenutačno uređivati ili prevesti vaš dokument s profesionalnim "
"formatiranjem i bojama. Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py:288
msgid ""
"AI: I can help you with formulas, data analysis, and colorful charts. Try me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu vam pomoći s formulama, analizom podataka i šarenim grafikonima. "
"Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py:289
msgid ""
"AI: I can help you create and edit polished, colorful shapes in Draw and "
"Impress. Try me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu vam pomoći stvoriti i uređivati uglađene, šarene oblike u Drawu i "
"Impressu. Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py:290
msgid ""
"AI: I can do web research to answer any question, or summarize a web page, "
"without seeing or changing your document. Let's chat."
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu obaviti istraživanje na webu kako bih odgovorio na bilo koje "
"pitanje ili sažeo web stranicu, bez pregledavanja ili mijenjanja vašeg "
"dokumenta. Razgovarajmo."

